text: MEET THE TEAM: Meet Shelley Vinson, RN! Shelley is one of the nurses giving #COVID19 #vaccine. Shelley works in the ER at Camden General Hospital when she’s not with us! “I’m thankful for what we’re doing here,” Vinson said. “I want to do my part in eradicating COVID-19.” https://t.co/sTLR2Yut24
